                        <h3>What is a Private Limited Company?</h3>
                        <p>A Private Limited Company is a privately held business entity, a popular choice for startups and growing businesses in India. It is governed by the Ministry of Corporate Affairs (MCA) under the Companies Act, 2013. This structure offers limited liability to its owners, meaning their personal assets are protected from business debts, and ensures the business has its own separate legal identity.</p>
