        <section class="accordion-section fade-in-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Everything You Need to Know</h2>
                <div class="accordion-container">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header">
                            Documents Required
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                                <img src="/assets/documents-plc.jpg" alt="Documents" class="accordion-img">
                                <p><strong>For Directors/Shareholders (Indian):</strong></p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Copy of PAN Card</li>
                                    <li>Copy of Aadhaar Card / Voter ID / Passport</li>
                                    <li>Latest Bank Statement / Utility Bill (address proof)</li>
                                    <li>Passport-sized Photograph</li>
                                </ul>
                                <br>
                                <p><strong>For the Registered Office Address:</strong></p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Latest Electricity Bill / Property Tax Receipt</li>
                                    <li>No Objection Certificate (NOC) from the property owner</li>
                                    <li>Rental Agreement (if rented)</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header">
                            Annual Compliance Checklist
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="accordion-content">
                            <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                                <img src="/assets/compliance-plc.jpeg" alt="Compliance" class="accordion-img">
                                <p>After incorporation, a company must fulfill these key compliances annually:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>Statutory Audit:</strong> Appointment of the first auditor within 30 days and conducting an annual audit of accounts.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Annual ROC Filings:</strong> Filing of financial statements (AOC-4) and Annual Return (MGT-7) with the MCA.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Income Tax Filing:</strong> Filing of annual Income Tax Return (ITR-6).</li>
                                    <li><strong>Board Meetings:</strong> A minimum of 4 board meetings must be held each year.</li>
                                    <li><strong>DIR-3 KYC:</strong> All directors must complete their annual KYC.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <button class="accordion-header">
                            Other Essential Registrations
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
