                            <div class="accordion-content-inner">
                                <img src="/assets/registrations-plc.jpg" alt="Registrations" class="accordion-img">
                                <p>Depending on your business, you may also need our assistance with:</p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li><strong>GST Registration:</strong> Mandatory if your turnover exceeds the prescribed limit.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Importer Exporter Code (IEC):</strong> Required for any import or export activities.</li>
                                    <li><strong>Trademark Registration:</strong> To protect your brand name and logo from being copied.</li>
                                    <li><strong>MSME/Udyam Registration:</strong> To avail benefits given to micro, small, and medium enterprises.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
